o\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even if this character was supposed to remain masked, the fact that everyone thinks that there is only a man or only men underneath, frustrated me a lot\\u2026 and I wanted to prove them wrong,' Ruel told Le Parisien.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruel_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.9904201974097189, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ruel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruel_(singer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruel_(singer)\"}, {\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Parisien\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this character\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"only a man or only men\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'A month and a half before the ceremony, Vincent Zenzel [the choreographer] contacted us, me and eight other guys, a month and a half before the ceremony, in very secret, very confidential conditions.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_van_Gogh\", \"score\": 0.9999761811167472, \"rank\": 2.3819433814292364e-05, \"text\": \"Vincent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_van_Gogh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_van_Gogh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'A month\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"the choreographer\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"eight other guys\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"very secret, very confidential conditions\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We knew very little about what we were going to do.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We learned in July that we would have two or three days of rehearsal, to be ready on July 26.'\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"two or three days\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"rehearsal\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ruel also revealed that she found it difficult to perform he acrobatics whilst holding the Olympic torch, which was 70cm tall and weighed 1.5kg.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ruel\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"acrobatics\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic torch\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"1.5kg\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The atmosphere was just crazy.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The atmosphere\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a lot of love and adrenaline, you felt like something big was happening,' said Ruel.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruel_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.9904201974097189, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ruel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruel_(singer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruel_(singer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"adrenaline\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1414}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did two stunts before I got the flame, which is very, very big, so it was almost impossible to do a jump with it.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two stunts\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"the flame\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"a jump\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We had this mask, a bit like a fencer\\u2026 but worse, it was like putting our heads in a colander.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this mask\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"our heads\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"a colander\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In the end, a compromise was found, to keep the guys hooked, so that everything was super safe.'\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"a compromise\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ruel also confirmed that she was the masked torchbearer once again during the Olympic Champions Parade in Paris earlier this month.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1892, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999770353, \"rank\": 2.2965779289630637e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ruel\", \"from\": 1786, \